  "description": [
    "Borah All Set to Seek ReElection as True Republican But Senator will first raise a little hell with G O P at Cleveland stooge candidate expected to step aside for Lion of Idaho Gov Landon unlikely to accept proposal to name Democrat as his running mate By RAYMOND CLAPPER Sen Borah it is suspected has his program definitely worked out now He is parking up for Cleveland There from his suite in the Hotel Cleveland he will yank the elephants tail until it hurts That will delight the spectators create work for the reporters and cause the victim to suffer some humiliation and pain At that point it is expected that Sen Borah will return to Idaho and run for reelection to the Senate as a true Repub hean if the national ticket isnt true Republican so much the worse for it In that case Sen Borah will devote himself exclusively to running for reelection without indicating by word or sign that he is aware of any presidential campaign The way for this is being prepared quietly Ray McKaig Idaho progressive Republican sometime ago became a chair warmer for his old friend and ally by an nouncing his senatorial candidacy"
  ],
